snippet.title: Sole Saga Gameplay Walkthrough / [No Commentary]
snippet.description:
Battle with the horde of monsters, Build your favorite hero with powerful skills and weapons in Action Roguelike style, Fight your way to the epic boss and become a legend.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2027970/Sole_Saga/

If you liked the video please remember to like & comment, I appreciate it a lot. Don't forget to subscribe.
